Aldric on the Station
[vignette dungeons/grainway_station]

"Grainway Station. Once all the grain caravans passed through here, wagons heavy with wheat. This was rich land, before the Retrenchment burned it to ash. The station was raised to supply the legions, a hard point on the line while we hunted Revathi raiders through the borderlands."

"That was before the retreat. Before the Iron. They hit fast and hard, the legion hardly had time to mount a defense, much less go on the march. Most of the stations have been picked clean over the years. This one…" he glances toward the sealed door, "This one we held."

"Until now."

